  "text": "Both results imply the non-existence of small breathers under the specified assumptions. The assumptions of Theorem 15 are not satisfied by the sine-Gordon equation, which is consistent with the existence of arbitrarily small breathers for this equation. We refer to [CITATION_1] , for a discussion on approximate breathers slowly radiating their energy, and to [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] for other closely related results of non-existence of breathers.",
